import React from 'react'
import bookDef from '../assets/data'

const EditPage = () => {
    let book = bookDef
    return (
        <form>
            <label>id:
                <input type="text" value={book.id}  onChange={(e)=> {setBook({...book, 'id':e.target.value})}}/>
            </label>
            <label>isbn:
                <input type="text" value={book.isbn}  onChange={(e)=> {setBook({...book, 'isbn':e.target.value})}}/>
            </label>
            <label>title:
                <input type="text" value={book.title}  onChange={(e)=> {setBook({...book, 'title':e.target.value})}}/>
            </label>
            <label>author:
                <input type="text" value={book.author.firstname}  onChange={(e)=> {setBook({...book, 'author.firstname':e.target.value})}}/>
                <input type="text" value={book.author.lastname}  onChange={(e)=> {setBook({...book, 'author.lastname':e.target.value})}}/>
            </label>
        </form>
    )
}

export default EditPage
